@@TJvCheckBox.HotTrackFont
Summary
  Font used when the mouse cursor is hovering over the control.
Description
  Use HotTrackFont to specify the font to be used instead of the normal font (ParentFont/ Control
  Font) when HotTrack is set to <B>True</B> and the mouse cursor is hovering over the control.
See Also
  TJvExCheckBox.OnMouseEnter, TJvExCheckBox.OnMouseLeave

