@@TJvCheckBox.Alignment
Summary
  Controls the horizontal placement of the text.
Description
  Set Alignment to specify how the text of the check box is justified within the ClientRect of the
  check box control.
  
  The effect of the Alignment property is more obvious if the WordWrap property is true and the check
  box includes more than one line of text.
See Also
  TJvCheckBox.Layout

